data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Cumming, nestled conveniently close to shopping, dining, and GA400! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and suburban charm. Step inside to discover a freshly painted interior that exudes warmth and elegance throughout. The first floor boasts a formal living room and formal dining room, ideal for hosting gatherings and special occasions. The great room with fireplace provides a cozy space to unwind with family and friends, while the eat-in kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Need a quiet space to work or study? Look no further than the office or flex space, perfectly situated on the first floor for added convenience. Retreat to the luxurious primary suite upstairs, complete with a private en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of room for family and guests, while the remaining bathrooms boast stylish finishes and modern amenities. Outside, you'll find a private fenced yard, perfect for enjoying the Georgia sunshine or hosting summer barbecues. And with a roof that's just a few years old, you can rest easy knowing that this home is not only stunning but also well-maintained. Located in the highly sought-after Forsyth County school district, this home offers unparalleled convenience and access to top-rated schools. Don't miss your chance to make this Cumming gem your own - schedule a showing today!
